@GarageStack.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5202
@VIN = YOUR_VIN_HERE

### List all vehicles
GET {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles
Accept: application/json

###

### Get vehicle capability config
GET {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/{{VIN}}/config
Accept: application/json

###

### Get latest telemetry snapshot
GET {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/{{VIN}}/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Get telemetry history (last 7 days by default)
GET {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/{{VIN}}/history
Accept: application/json

###

### Get trip history (last 30 days by default)
GET {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/{{VIN}}/trips
Accept: application/json

###

### Get distinct MQTT topics seen for a vehicle (diagnostic)
GET {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/{{VIN}}/topics
Accept: application/json

###

### Send a command -- lock the vehicle
POST {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/{{VIN}}/commands/lock
Content-Type: application/json

{ "value": "1" }

###

### Send a command -- start climate control
POST {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vehicles/{{VIN}}/commands/climate
Content-Type: application/json

{ "value": "on" }

###

### Get VAPID public key for push notifications
GET {{GarageStack.Api_HostAddress}}/api/push/vapid-public-key
Accept: application/json

###
